Description: An intimidating presence, the Fifth Brother Inquisitor is tasked to hunt down Force-sensitive survivors. A man of few words, he uses his powerful physicality and brute strength to pry leads from cowering citizens, leading to the capture of elusive Jedi. Trained in the dark side of the Force, he wields a dual-bladed lightsaber, reveling in the opportunity to destroy rebels and Force-wielders alike.
